                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     Epsom Derby 
                          
	Epsom: Jim Bolger-trained New Approach lifted the Vodafone Derby here on Saturday. K. J. Manning partnered the 5-1 shot to half-a-length victory over an equally fancied horse, Tartan Bearer. (Reuters)                                                                                                                                                                       
